<h3>Build Topic Clusters</h3>
<p>Organize keywords by topic. Create pillar pages for broad terms. Create cluster pages for specific terms.</p>
<p><strong>Example cluster:</strong>
- Pillar: "SEO Guide"
- Cluster: "keyword research", "on-page SEO", "technical SEO", "link building"</p>
<h3>Prioritize by Business Value</h3>
<p>Not all keywords are worth targeting. Prioritize based on business impact.</p>
